title: 175: Draft preview conference call
itunes:title: 175: Draft preview conference call
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks meet with NFL media across the country for a conference call previewing the 2017 NFL Draft. The guys break down the top prospects, give their own draft strategies and debate whether there is a quarterback worth taking in the top 10.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
